  "type": "feat",
  "img": "systems/pf1/icons/skills/affliction_04.jpg",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a standard action, you can make a melee touch attack that causes a living creature to become <em>shaken</em> for a number of rounds equal to 1/2 your wizard level (minimum 1). If you touch a <em>shaken</em> creature with this ability, it becomes <em>frightened</em> for 1 round if it has fewer Hit Dice than your wizard level. You can use this ability a number of times per day equal to 3 + your <em>Intelligence</em> modifier.</p>"
